<h1>About <i>The Banker</i></h1>
<p>The Banker is a database-less Rails app that utilizing the <a href="https://currencyconverterapi.com">Currency Converter API</a> to quicky convert USD, EUR, and SGD currencies. Exchange rates are cached and refreshed every minute to provide up-to-the-minute exchange rates without exhausting the API rate limit.</p>